@startuml
title Weather Station System State Machine

[*] --> ShutDown
state ShutDown
ShutDown : do / restart system

state ConfigMode
ConfigMode : entry / configuration mode
ConfigMode : do / configure system
ConfigMode : exit / return to running state

state Running
Running : entry / collect data
Running : do / collect data
Running : exit / return to running state

state Controlled
Controlled : entry / remote control
Controlled : do / control system
Controlled : exit / return to running state

state ShutDown
ShutDown : entry / shutdown command
ShutDown : do / shut down system

state DataCollection
DataCollection : entry / collect data
DataCollection : do / collect data
DataCollection : exit / return to running state

state SummaryPreparation
SummaryPreparation : entry / prepare summary
SummaryPreparation : do / prepare summary
SummaryPreparation : exit / return to running state

state StatusChecking
StatusChecking : entry / check status
StatusChecking : do / check status
StatusChecking : exit / return to running state

ShutDown --> ConfigMode : restart
ConfigMode --> Running : configuration complete
Running --> DataCollection : clock triggered
DataCollection --> Running : data collection complete
Running --> SummaryPreparation : summary request
SummaryPreparation --> Running : summary prepared
Running --> StatusChecking : status request
StatusChecking --> Running : status checked
Running --> Controlled : remote control
Controlled --> Running : remote control released
ConfigMode --> Running : configuration complete
ShutDown --> [*] : shut down system
@enduml
